105
00:05:59,354 --> 00:06:00,678
Merry Christmas, Plagg.

106
00:06:00,739 --> 00:06:02,358
Merry Christmas, Adrien.

107
00:06:08,013 --> 00:06:08,902
Adrien?

108
00:06:10,323 --> 00:06:11,519
Adrien?

109
